Love's a Bitch;;94;;93;;R;;"Amores Perros" is a bold, intensely emotional, and ambitious story of lives that collide in a Mexico City car crash. Inventively structured as a triptych of overlapping and intersecting narratives, "Amores Perros" explores the lives of disparate characters who are catapulted into unforeseen dramatic situations instigated by the seemingly inconsequential destiny of a dog named Cofi.;;Mystery & thriller,Drama;;Alejandro González Iñárritu;;2000;;Emilio Echevarría,Gael García Bernal,Goya Toledo,Álvaro Guerrero,Vanessa Bauche,Jorge Salinas,Marco Pérez,Rodrigo Murray;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/amores_perros